step-def: Given I add an item to Aircraft

    step: When I wait until the element <<id=redButton>> is present
    step: When I click the element <<id=redButton>>
    step: When I wait until the element <<name=name>> is visible
    step: When I type <<///>> into the field <<name=name>>
    step: When I click the element <<name=addBtn>>
    step: Then the element <<dmMessage>> should be absent
    step: When I clear the text from the field <<name=name>>
    step: When I type <<X-Wing>> into the field <<name=name>>
    step: When I click the element <<name=addBtn>>
    step: When I wait until the text of element <<name=dmMessage>> should be <<Aircraft Added>>
